title: Cozy Spacious Apartment, W/D In Unit, FREE Carport Parking, POOL🎈🌞
posting_body: Welcome home to The Commons at Federal Way
The Commons at Federal Way apartment community is situated in the lush backdrop of beautiful Northwest landscape and peaceful surroundings.
Featuring spacious one and two bedroom floor plans, each outfitted with tasteful cabinetry, inviting wood burning fireplaces and plentiful storage.

Spectacular wooded and private views, along with an updated community center, onsite management and 24 hour maintenance are only a few of the many amenities you will experience at The Commons at Federal Way.
Bordering Panther Lake Park our community is just minutes from Celebration Park, St. Francis Community Hospital & convenient to shopping.
Easy access to I-5, SR 167, & Highway 18.
Live in the perfect location with convenient access to restaurants, local conveniences and entertainment.
Come experience what quality service and a comfortable home feels like at The Commons.
This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 700 Sq.
